maintext:
HARRISBURG, Pa. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Thursday afternoon’s drawing of the Pennsylvania Lottery’s “Treasure Hunt” game were:
07-08-23-27-29
(seven, eight, twenty-three, twenty-seven, twenty-nine)
Estimated jackpot: $10,000
